Steam’s Halloween Sale 2019 is now live, offering big discounts on hundreds of titles across the storefront. These discounts will be available from 28 October until 1 November and will not change for the duration of the sale. Steam’s Halloween 2019 sale includes hefty price cuts on popular titles such as Grand Theft Auto V, The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt, Monster Hunter: World, Fallout 4, and many other games. A selection of horror-themed titles is also heavily discounted, including Hunt: Showdown, Resident Evil 2, Dead by Daylight, and Prey. The PC gaming storefront will also offer price cuts on a variety of games which have special Halloween-themed updates or in-game events with a Halloween theme. Valve has categorised horror and Halloween-themed games on its event page, offering gamers an easy way to browse everything from free-to-play titles with Halloween-themed events to virtual reality horror games. Below is a selection of popular PC games which have been discounted for the Steam Halloween Sale. The full list of discounted games can be found on the Steam Store. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-325149" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Destiny-2-Forsaken-640x360.jpg" alt="Destiny 2 Forsaken" width="640" height="360" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Destiny-2-Forsaken-640x360.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Destiny-2-Forsaken-600x338.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Destiny-2-Forsaken-768x432.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Destiny-2-Forsaken.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-325151" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/GTA-V-640x360.jpg" alt="GTA V" width="640" height="360" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uplo